{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotations:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","symbolKind":"method","title":"addAnnotations:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addAnnotations:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapSnapshotter(im)addAnnotations:","role":"symbol"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","text":"NSArray<id<MLNAnnotation>>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotations","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotations","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An array of annotation objects. Each object in the array","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"must conform to the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol. The snapshotter retains each","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotation object.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cannot be added to the snapshotter at this time. Nor can "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects that are not instances of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". Any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"multipoint, multipolyline, multipolygon, or shape collection objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are specified are silently ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotations:"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Adds an array of annotations to the snapshotter.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolyline":{"title":"MLNPolyline","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of two or more vertices,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"specified as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"text":" instances, and the line segments that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use an polyline to represent a road or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path along which something moves.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolyline","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolyline"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" generates static raster images of the map. Each snapshot"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"image depicts a portion of a map defined by an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you provide. The snapshotter generates an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"asynchronously, calling "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" methods if defined, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"passing it into a completion handler once tiles and other resources needed for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the snapshot are finished loading."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotter"}],"title":"MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional methods about significant events when creating a snapshot using an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter"},{"type":"text","text":" object."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotterdelegate","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapSnapshotterDelegate","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMultiPolyline","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline"},{"text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolyline"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotOptions":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotoptions","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotOptions","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapSnapshotOptions","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The options to use when creating images with the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPoint":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is an abstract superclass used to define shapes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"composed of multiple vertices.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipoint","type":"topic","title":"MLNMultiPoint","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPoint","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshotter/addAnnotations:":{"abstract":[{"text":"Adds an array of annotations to the snapshotter.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshotter\/addannotations:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshotter\/addAnnotations:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"addAnnotations:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"addAnnotations:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapSnapshot":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An image generated by a snapshotter object."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapSnapshot","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapsnapshot","type":"topic","title":"MLNMapSnapshot","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMapSnapshot"}]}}}